    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p>During execution of Universal Enrollment flow, <b>Account owner mailing address is not found in the Review/Submit page</b>, causing assertion failure in automation during verification step:</p>

<blockquote><p><em>“User verifies information on submit page for &lt;test case name&gt;”</em></p></blockquote>

<p>This issue is consistently observed for <b>NYD plan</b>, while <b>NMD plan passes for same scenario</b>.</p>

<hr />

<h3><a name="Environment%3A"></a><b>Environment:</b></h3>

<ul>
	<li>Application: Universal Enrollment</li>
	<li>Plan: NYD (New York 529)</li>
	<li>Environment: Stage</li>
	<li>Feature: <tt>UniversalEnrollmentPositive.feature</tt></li>
</ul>


<hr />

<h3><a name="StepstoReproduce%3A"></a><b>Steps to Reproduce:</b></h3>

<ol>
	<li>Start enrollment for NYD Individual Account</li>
	<li>Select <b>NOSAMEADDR</b> (Different mailing address)</li>
	<li>Enter mailing address on Account Owner Address page</li>
	<li>Continue with funding (Bank / Contribution flow)</li>
	<li>Navigate to <b>Review/Submit page</b></li>
	<li>Verify Account Owner Mailing Address</li>
</ol>


<hr />

<h3><a name="ActualResult%3A"></a><b>Actual Result:</b></h3>

<ul>
	<li>❌ Mailing address from test data (e.g., <tt>ADDRLINE1_AO_MAIL</tt>) is <b>not found in Review section</b></li>
	<li>Assertion failure occurs:</li>
</ul>


<div class="preformatted panel" style="border-width: 1px;"><div class="preformattedContent panelContent">
<pre>java.lang.AssertionError: Account owner mailing address not found in review section expected [true] but found [false]
</pre>
</div></div>

<hr />

<h3><a name="ExpectedResult%3A"></a><b>Expected Result:</b></h3>

<ul>
	<li>✅ Mailing address entered on Account Owner Address page should be <b>displayed correctly in Review/Submit section</b></li>
</ul>


<hr />

